        <h2 class="display-5 link-body-emphasis mb-1">What Happens to Your Old Smartphone? A Journey Through E-Waste Recycling</h2>
        <p class="blog-post-meta">January 2, 2025 by Teng Yik Shen</p>
        <p>Ever wondered what happens to your smartphone after you toss it into a recycling bin or trade it in? This blog takes you on a journey through the life of a discarded smartphone, revealing how responsible e-waste recycling works and why it's crucial for our environment and economy.</p>
        <hr>

